http://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/technology/internet/Yahoo-Messenger-rolls-out-new-video-sharing-feature/article14581525.ece

New Delhi Yahoo on Tuesday announced a new feature of sharing videos on its instant messaging platform Yahoo Messenger.The new feature is just like sending photos. When composing a message, tap to choose a video from your device’s video gallery. The user needs to trim videos to a minute or less before sharing in Yahoo Messenger.The Yahoo Messenger app can be downloaded through iOS App store and Google Play store.